Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveEx-Big Brother Naija housemate, Tope Adenibuyan popularly known as Teddy A, on Saturday celebrated his wife and mother of his two children, Oluwabamike Olawunmi referred to as “BamBam” on the occassion of her birthday.
Celebrating her birthday, Teddy A shared throwback photos of them in the BBNaija house and others of Bambam outside of the house.He said in his Instagram post, “New year, new age but still the same sweet you. You get better with age like fine wine. My wife, my life, my lover, my rare fabric forever.
“It’s world Bammy day, happy birthday my Queen.”
